name: Natural Codex 1
description: There is a space near my home where three trees have grown a little too close together, each blocking the sun from the inner sides of the other. In between, mushrooms grow and the Mule Deer sleep. It is its own ecosystem, written differently from the lawns and xeroscapes of nearby yards. Created from a lidar scan using an open source device that was 3d printed and using a RPi.
